This class is used to create map using game console commands.

A class to handle reading data from the map
MapValidation
The class is used to create the map validation to check the if the map is a map which is strongly connected or not and to check if there are any continents without country or countries without any neighbors.

A class to test all the functionalities in Map Validation
Order

A class to create Orders in the game.
OrderInfo
A class with the information of Order details
Player

Reinforcement

SaveMap
